    <h1>About This Project</h1>
    <section class="general">
        <h3>General</h3>
        <p>This project is an implementation of the Yelp Camp project from Colt Steele's course <a
                href="https://www.udemy.com/course/the-web-developer-bootcamp/" target="_blank">The Web Developer Bootcamp 2024</a>.
            <small>(Note: The title suggests it's updated for 2024, but it's misleading)</small>
        </p>
        <p>While generally following the course, there are a few deviations in this implementation. The main differences
            are
            listed below.</p>
        <p>Deployed in June 2024, it is planned to be maintained until December 2024, with live deployment until June
            2025.
            Please note that all data and locations are fictional.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="stack">
        <h3>Tools Used</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Node.js - JavaScript runtime for server-side development.</li>
            <li>Express - Web application framework.</li>
