            <li>Mongoose - MongoDB object modeling for Node.js.</li>
            <li>Bootstrap - Front-end framework.</li>
            <li>Cloudinary - Image upload and management service (proprietary).</li>
            <li>Passport.js - Authentication middleware.</li>
            <li>MapLibre - Open-source mapping library.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

